-------------------------------------
#Compiling
-------------------------------------

##jtalk.c

gcc -c jtalk.c -lpthread

gcc -g -o client jtalk.o -lpthread libfdr.a

##jtalk_server.c

gcc jtalk_server.c-lpthread -o server

------------------------------------
#Running
------------------------------------

./server [host] [port]

./client [host] [port]
************************************
-NOT: "i386 architecture of input file `libfdr.a(fields.o)' is incompatible with i386:x86-64 output" hatasý ile karþýlaþýlýrsa
libfdr.a yeniden derlenmelidir.

